Costly							KEY:Costly																				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable																																																																																													DESC:(12 CP). Costly makes it harder to affect you with mystical abilities of some type (typically Arcane magic, Psionics, Thaumaturgy and Dweomer, Witchcraft, or Divine magic). - Magical effects cost 1 extra spell level to affect you properly. The spell still functions either way, but if the caster does not spend the extra level (they can sacrifice any available spell level or generic levels), the magical effect is weakened, lowering the required saving throw DC (if any) and effective Caster Level by -1. - Psionic and Witchcraft abilities require 2 extra Power (easier to get than spare spell levels), but if the user cannot pay, they are simply drained of all remaining Power and the effect fails.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									COST:12	SOURCEPAGE:p.28
Costly / Improved						KEY:Costly ~ Improved								OUTPUTNAME:Costly ~ Improved						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Costly																																																																																	DESC:(+12 CP) increases the extra cost to 2 spell levels or 4 Power.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			COST:12	SOURCEPAGE:p.28
