Create Artifact						KEY:Create Artifact ~ Eclipse																	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable.ItemCreation																																																																																											DESC:(6 CP) You may create magical items the old-fashioned way, with bizarre mystic ingredients, strange rituals, and guesswork. While very powerful, and supremely flexible, this is laborious, dangerous, and unreliable, which is why modern methods supplanted it. Occasional adventurers, whether in search of supreme power, or simply because they prefer the quests and mysticism of such creations to spending time and effort to learn modern methods, still study such antiquities.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.28
