Create Item / Artisan					KEY:Create Item ~ Artisan							OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Artisan					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+6 CP) allows you to half the XP cost of an enchantment by doubling the GP cost or vice-versa. At the GM's option this may be automatic (half GP and double XP) on Tattoo Magic/Creature Enchantments. As an alternative, the item may be assigned unpleasant or dangerous side effects rather than doubling a cost.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Transference				KEY:Create Item ~ Transference						OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Transference				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+6 CP) allows you to accept freely donated experience points for making magical items instead of supplying them all yourself, although you cannot use such donated points for any other purpose. You can also put spirits into items to power them; this provides the equivalent of (200 x creature's CR) XP. As a rule, spirits are only willing if the binding is for a limited time. For an additional +6 CP you may bind unwilling spirits or drain XP from unwilling victims. Unfortunately, items created in this fashion are invariably cursed in some fashion. Secondarily, binding spirits into items often upsets more powerful entities.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Epic					KEY:Create Item ~ Epic								OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Epic						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																PREPCLEVEL:MIN=20																														DESC:(+12 CP, minimum character level 20) lets you create items up to twice as powerful as normal ones. Multiply the base GP cost by 10 for making such items.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				COST:12	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Excellence				KEY:Create Item ~ Excellence							OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Excellence					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+3 CP) lets you add your full attribute bonus to the DC of resisting an item's functions rather than the minimum bonus required to cast the spell.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Harvest of Artifice			KEY:Create Item ~ Harvest of Artifice					OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Harvest of Artifice			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+6 CP) lets you gather and expend up to 100 XP (+50 per additional +3 CP) per month on item creation or Transmutations (below) at no personal cost. You cannot add these points to your personal total, accumulate them from month to month, or use them for other purposes.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Alchemic Mastery			KEY:Create Item ~ Alchemic Mastery						OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Alchemic Mastery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+3 CP) lets you distill XP (whether personal, donated or harvested) into alchemical mixtures. These function as universal power components, storing those XP for later use by anyone in making items, transmuting, or in casting spells with XP components. Unfortunately, it costs 2 XP to store 1 and the stored points cannot be used for other purposes.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Create Item / Transmutation				KEY:Create Item ~ Transmutation						OUTPUTNAME:Create Item ~ Transmutation				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:General.EclipseAbilityOutput.Abilities.Corruptable					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Create Item																																																																																DESC:(+6 CP) lets you infuse XP into material to transmute it into more useful mundane forms. This costs 1 XP per 2 GP worth of equipment so produced. We recommend that this be limited to transmutations within the same general type of elemental material and that "labor costs" be considered for things like opening pits.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
