Amorphous						KEY:Amorphous ~ Eclipse					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:EclipseAbilityOutput.TemplatesRacial.Corruptable	DESC:(6 CP). Your body has no definite form, and can squeeze through cracks, into oddly-shaped spaces. You cannot be flanked since you have no facing, implicit or otherwise. Amorphous characters usually also purchase immunity to the extra damage from critical hits and nonflanking sneak attacks. This is not required though.																																																																																																																																																								COST:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.61
